Source: libimage-base-tk-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5)
Maintainer: Kevin Ryde <user42@zip.com.au>
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://user42.tuxfamily.org/image-base-tk/index.html
Bugs: mailto:user42@zip.com.au

Package: libimage-base-tk-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: libimage-base-perl (>= 1.12), perl-tk, ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: libtk-tiff-perl, libtk-canvasfig-perl
Description: Draw into Tk photo or canvas
 An Image::Base extension to operate on Tk::Photo images and
 Tk::Canvas widgets.
 .
 Tk::Photo can read and write various file formats, including PNG,
 JPEG, XPM, XBM, GIF, BMP, PPM/PGM, and TIFF with Tk::TIFF from
 libtk-tiff-perl.  Tk::Canvas can write (but not read) postscript EPS,
 and with Tk::CanvasFig (libtk-canvasfig-perl) xfig format too.
